{"tid":1549672,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[驚世] 非標題黨，我希望我係多心。。。","createTime":"2019-09-07T11:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T12:02:35.000Z","uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a31b911aa9a4f7d1a85f1a160d3a2cd36e3a8547","tid":1549672,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:46:15.000Z","msg":"民主人權法案通過之日即將到來，<br />\n<br />\n但係，我地嘅制裁名單中嘅人，點解好似無乜特別風聲顯示佢地因爲驚而採取行動嘅新聞嘅呢？<br />\n<br />\n另外，特區政府亦無咩特別明顯嘅小動作，去回應對呢個法案嘅恐懼嘅呢？<br />\n<br />\n總括而言，我想講嘅係，點解佢地好似唔驚咁嘅？真係咁老定？<br />\n<br />\n利申: 我絕對希望自己係多心，各位手足如果頭腦清晰啲嘅請話我知我係諗多左"},{"pid":"e1259b28215f81a091cbc7bccb5edc959a3f0402","tid":1549672,"uid":194454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:47:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">睇下呢本外國文宣啊求下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n[重開] 美國就快復會！！快啲推比外國人睇！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549540</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c950591e09994f32a7770bbc1387fc86854e74c2","tid":1549672,"uid":102619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"無咖 佢地唔驚我地聽日都照去"},{"pid":"d791fc8491bbd3359f3ef2a833a80da8efe8726c","tid":1549672,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:48:22.000Z","msg":"借之前一個巴打寫嘅文一用<br />\n<br />\n佢哋大搖大擺行出警察宿舍，<br />\n每一個警察行過，都陰陰嘴笑鳩你班香港人：<br />\n「光復香港喎，時代革命喎。」<br />\n「曱甴。」<br />\n<br />\n每一個圍過警署嘅街坊，<br />\n都要接受依一班警察，<br />\n仲有佢哋家屬嘅冷眼。<br />\n「嗰隻甴曱啊，」佢指住你，<br />\n「嗰日佢咪圍鳩咗喺到囉，<br />\n依家咪死狗咁。」<br />\n<br />\n你忍唔住，你屌鳩佢老母。<br />\n不過佢一啲都無怕過你，<br />\n「甴曱！收皮啦！你打鳩我啊？！」<br />\n佢行埋嚟，再摸下你個頭，<br />\n「戇鳩仔。」<br />\n你忍住，你知道你唔可能打返佢。<br />\n佢拍拍你塊臉，<br />\n「點啊？你唔打鳩我喇？」<br />\n佢一啲收手嘅意欲都無，<br />\n因為警察已經為所欲為：<br />\n「又話黑警死全家？我全家仲喺到喎。」<br />\n<br />\n宿舍隔離就係警署，<br />\n警察一嚟到就會將你搭入去。<br />\n無人知道裏面會發生咩事。<br />\n你可能會畀人打一身、<br />\n畀人彈春袋、玩屎忽。<br />\n你女朋友喺你隔離，<br />\n你唔知道佢畀人拉埋入去之後會發生咩事，<br />\n你保護唔到你女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n「我要你同我道歉。」<br />\n警察一家望實你，同你講。<br />\n你唔敢再生事端。<br />\n「對唔住，好對唔住。」<br />\n最後你向警察道歉。<br />\n佢一邊拍你塊臉，一邊同你講，<br />\n「下次唔好喇。」<br />\n你覺得好興幸，<br />\n警察肯原諒你。<br />\n<br />\n依一個就係香港人放棄嘅結局，<br />\n你班「曱甴」依家想放棄未？"},{"pid":"789305e9364597bba9e1d727d7f6a50027f60d70","tid":1549672,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c950591e09994f32a7770bbc1387fc86854e74c2","tid":1549672,"uid":102619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"無咖 佢地唔驚我地聽日都照去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"咁當然啦，點都出啊！<br />\n<br />\n只係我好奇怪佢地憑乜咁老定啫"},{"pid":"2c5e03a9b1084adfd37d69b322269075dcbec450","tid":1549672,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:48:57.000Z","msg":"你點樣得出政府唔驚法案呢個結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf3773b7329c6cb55b1184b07680cd92f1f4056","tid":1549672,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"依家咪想拉曬所有人囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1108bfe248dd45c86b18619569e2a6894fd107db","tid":1549672,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"借po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［拋磚］一人N個聽日用嘅英文口號<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549609</a>"},{"pid":"8d3e2b2dda224a8342657dde7a68b74acc83b015","tid":1549672,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5e03a9b1084adfd37d69b322269075dcbec450","tid":1549672,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:48:57.000Z","msg":"你點樣得出政府唔驚法案呢個結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:51:00.000Z","msg":"其實我應該咁講，事實係，佢地無乜小動作，連掙札都無，我覺得好撚怪"},{"pid":"9c71a66a9b230e6bbe62016c1e164fe7c1893426","tid":1549672,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:51:07.000Z","msg":"10月中美重啓貿易談判，呢個亦可疑"},{"pid":"836a2fa7383b97c881ce434b01e223069cb40504","tid":1549672,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"咁點呀,佢地唔驚係咪就唔理吖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b25a4676c8d49465a68241ad0be139a7e96e77","tid":1549672,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbf3773b7329c6cb55b1184b07680cd92f1f4056","tid":1549672,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"依家咪想拉曬所有人囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:51:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲之前都做緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca07d56e5d48437e838c56b83ec6d4d5a10e1c0","tid":1549672,"uid":303210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"836a2fa7383b97c881ce434b01e223069cb40504","tid":1549672,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"咁點呀,佢地唔驚係咪就唔理吖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:52:42.000Z","msg":"都話唔係咯，都話點都出咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1dd73d9e3481c3280c8789970ed551debfdebd","tid":1549672,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>九月八，遮打見！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZUq8PfJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp